# Anonymous users can read/write most topics except internal and admin-specific topics
topic readwrite sensors/#
topic readwrite logs/#
topic readwrite alerts/#
topic readwrite data/#
topic readwrite network/#
topic readwrite security/#
topic readwrite monitoring/#

# Deny anonymous access to internal and admin-specific topics
topic deny internal/#
topic deny admin/#
topic deny credentials/#
topic deny system/#

# Only admin_user can access the hidden internal topic and admin-specific topics
user admin_user
topic readwrite internal/#
topic readwrite admin/#
topic readwrite credentials/#
topic readwrite system/#